iorange</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/dym/148.gif\" />要死了","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"14080","username":"shimotsuki14","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"13591","dbdateline":"1450636646","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"31079008","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"巴啦啦小兔兔儿","authorid":"431781","dateline":"2015-12-21 10:13","message":"昨天看了看animestyle那个京吹专题果然后面的摄影监督高尾一也以及花田大先生的访谈也是非常有意思<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face/151.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超喜欢下雨天的武本看到第七话精彩的雨水特效之后兴奋的不能自已，直接给高尾打电话了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face/94.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201512/21/101213s0rzubs08anzbvdr.jpg\" attach=\"31079008\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n从原作到剧本到最后的动画台词，每一次都是精炼凝缩和加深气氛的过程，花田对他最后创造的这个hentai台词十分自豪<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face/161.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201512/21/101221g88vwrfwxrvmzkrx.jpg\" attach=\"31079008\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n结果山田学丽奈摸石原鼻子的事儿原来是全社都知道的<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face/12.gif\" /><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201512/21/101228onsq28qf9tddtq4n.jpg\" attach=\"31079008\" /></div><br />\r\n石原：不要听风就是雨，你这么说就等于……在这件事上你也有责任吧<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face/91.gif\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"14081","username":"巴啦啦小兔兔儿","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"13592","dbdateline":"1450663986","attachments":[],"imagelist":[],"groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"31079300","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"lostinyume","authorid":"179604","dateline":"2015-12-21 10:38","message":"叶月如果改成胡桃那种傲娇元气双马尾的话人气也会up up得多吧","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"14082","username":"lostinyum